law.history: Repealed 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 37, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1994. -- Created 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 71, sec. 9, effective July 15, 1988.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Assignment by LRC to subcommittee -- Public meeting -- Reports required -- Expiration of administrative regulations -- Enactment into statute -- Prohibition concerning promulgation.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/94). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 37 prevails over its amendment in 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 486.
